  "description": "<p>Details:</p><p>Location: Jurong</p><p>Working hours: Monday - Friday Office Hours</p><p>Salary: Up to $2,700</p><p>1 Year Contract (Extendable)<br /></p><p>Duties:</p><ul><li>Assist with daily warehouse operations, such as receiving, sorting, packing, and shipping goods</li><li>Ensure accurate handling of incoming and outgoing goods, and maintain proper records</li><li>Stock and remove items from shelves, keeping the warehouse clean and organized</li><li>Operating of forklift</li><li>Conduct inventory counts and help verify that stock levels match system data</li><li>Inspect product quality and report any damage or irregularities</li><li>Assist with loading and unloading goods, ensuring safe handling</li><li>Follow the company’s warehouse procedures and safety regulations</li></ul><p></p><p>Requirements:</p><ul><li>Experience in warehouse or logistics-related work</li><li>Possess Forklift License</li></ul><p></p><p>Interested Applicants, please click Apply Now</p><p><br /><br />Chow Zi Qing<br />R2199258<br />Revup Proservices Pte Ltd<br />EA.24C2366</p>",
